      {
        "id": "amalthea_courage_story",
        "type": "story",
        "text": "\"I've been trying to control my visions more directly. It's been working, but there's just... too many of them. I lose the details if I try to take it all in. How would y'all decide which visions are the most important ones?\""
      },
      {
        "id": "amalthea_courage_choice",
        "text": "The investigators must decide (choose one):",
        "type": "input",
        "input": {
          "type": "choose_one",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "purity",
              "text": "\"Focus on using the visions to keep us protected.\"",
              "steps": [
                "amalthea_purity_story",
                "amalthea_purity_swap"
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "resolve",
              "text": "\"Focus on using the visions to fight these monsters.\"",
              "effects": [
                "amalthea_resolve_story",
                "amalthea_resolve_swap"
              ]
            }
          ]
        } 
      },
      {
        "id": "amalthea_purity_story",
        "type": "story",
        "text": "Thea nods, folding the book with a serene smile. \"I'll do exactly that. Even though I'm the one supposed to be guiding you, you've given me plenty of guidance. But it's my turn for sure now. We'll be ready for anything they can cook up.\""
      },
