      {
        "id": "amalthea_wisdom_story",
        "type": "story",
        "text": "\"I've been trying to open myself up to my visions more, let them play out fully and reveal things I didn't see before.\nI just... don't know how to interpret them. What would you do with the visions and the prophecies?\""
      },
      {
        "id": "amalthea_wisdom_choice",
        "text": "The investigators must decide (choose one):",
        "type": "input",
        "input": {
          "type": "choose_one",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "enlightenment",
              "text": "\"Try to square the visions with the written prophecy.\"",
              "steps": [
                "amalthea_enlightenment_story",
                "amalthea_enlightenment_swap"
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "mystery",
              "text": "\"Take the visions as they are, beyond the prophecy.\"",
              "effects": [
                "amalthea_mystery_story",
                "amalthea_mystery_swap"
              ]
            }
          ]
        } 
      },
      {
        "id": "amalthea_enlightenment_story",
        "type": "story",
        "text": "Thea casts her eyes back down toward the tome. \"I'll do exactly that. Even though I'm the one supposed to be guiding you, you've given me plenty of guidance. But it's my turn for sure now. We'll make sure this prophecy goes exactly to plan.\""
